BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 210.0 670 Td (What Is Mindfulness?) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 580 Td (Mindfulness means paying attention to the present moment on purpose,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 562 Td (without judgment. It means noticing what is happening RIGHT NOW - what you) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 544 Td (see, hear, feel, and think - without trying to change it. Your mind) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 526 Td (naturally wanders to the past \(worrying about what happened\) or future) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 508 Td (\(worrying about what might happen\). Mindfulness brings you back to NOW,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 490 Td (where life actually happens. It is a skill anyone can learn with practice!) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
