BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 544 Td (slows, and your brain gets more oxygen. Here are 5 breathing techniques: 1\)) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 526 Td (Belly Breathing \(hand on belly, breathe so it rises\), 2\) 4-7-8 Breathing) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 508 Td (\(in 4, hold 7, out 8\), 3\) Box Breathing \(in 4, hold 4, out 4, hold 4\), 4\)) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 490 Td (Bunny Breathing \(3 quick sniffs in, 1 long out\), 5\) Flower & Candle \(smell) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 472 Td (flower in, blow candle out\).) Tj ET

