BT 0.4 g /F1 14 Tf 275.76 720 Td (CHAPTER 7) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 171.6 670 Td (Dealing with Worry Mindfully) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 580 Td (Everyone worries sometimes. But worry is about the FUTURE - things that) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 562 Td (haven't happened \(and usually won't!\). Mindfulness helps with worry by) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 544 Td (bringing you back to the present, where you are safe. Instead of fighting) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 526 Td (worry or pushing it away, mindfulness teaches you to NOTICE it, name it) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 508 Td (\('Oh, that's worry'\), and let it pass like a cloud in the sky.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
